  "$note": "Golden cases for the Unified Gap Engine (eval:gap). Each case runs cv_skills + jd_requirements through the REAL SkillNormalizer → SkillDiffService, overlays a fixture evidence ledger, then asserts buildGapItems() produces the expected canonical gap items. Offline, 0 LLM. Data-sanity: every cv_skills name MUST normalize.",
